What you need to know:  Trae Young scored 47 points to lead Atlanta over Indiana 131-128 while Marcus Morris scored 31 points to lead the Los Angeles Clippers over host Detroit 106-102.Ja Morant had 17 points and 10 assists for Memphis in a 125-118 triumph at Oklahoma City while Jonas Valanciunas had 32 points in New Orleans' 130-105 victory over Houston.